.DT
add_criminal
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_criminal

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_criminal -  This method adds a player into the criminals array
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_criminal(string place_name,
mixed player,
int type)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^place_name%^RESET%^ - the name of the place to add the criminal in
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - the name or object of the player to add
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of offense.  They have been defined as follows -
       VANDALISM  1 - vandalism
       THEFT      2 - stealing
       SHOPLIFT   3 - shoplifting
       SLAUGHTER  4 - killing innocents
       RESIST     5 - resisting arrest
       GUARDKILL  6 - guard killing
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if successfully added, 0 if not
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/crime_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a player into the criminals array
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
"/include/crime.h"

.EP

